  "identifier": "HCR 23",
  "title": "A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION directing the establishment of the Property Taxation Task Force.",
  "abstract": "Direct the Legislative Research Commission to establish the Property Taxation Task Force to study, review, and provide policy recommendations on how to address local property taxation increases; require the task force to meet monthly during the 2026 legislative interim; outline task force membership; require the task force to submit its findings and recommendations to the Legislative Research Commission by December 1, 2026.",
